STATE
v.
Leo KEARNEY 294P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 2, 2019

Leo Kearney, For Kearney, Leo

Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of N.C.

Robert A. Evans, Jr., District Attorney, For State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 2nd of August 2019 by Defendant for Extension of Time to File Federal Habeas Corpus Petition:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd of August 2019."
